---
import Layout from '../../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Unexplained Fatigue: Could Your Heart Be the Cause? — Dr Delhasse" description="Persistent fatigue may be linked to a heart condition. Heart failure, rhythm disorders: discover the cardiac causes of fatigue." lang="en">

  <section class="hero-page">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Unexplained <span class="text-primary">Fatigue</span></h1>
      <p class="hero-sub">Could your heart be the cause?</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container detail-content">
      <img src="/images/svg/symptomes/Fatiga.svg" alt="Fatigue" class="detail-icon" />

      <p>In cardiology, fatigue often reflects a mismatch between the body's oxygen needs and supply. Heart failure reduces cardiac output, leading to poor perfusion of organs such as muscles and the brain. This results in a lack of energy and cognitive slowing.</p>

      <p>Rhythm disorders impair ventricular function and reduce haemodynamic efficiency, causing fluctuating fatigue, sometimes associated with dizziness. Myocardial ischaemia limits the heart's energy reserves, worsening the sensation of exhaustion during exertion.</p>

      <p>When faced with unexplained and persistent fatigue, a cardiac evaluation is recommended.</p>

      <div class="detail-cta">
        <a href="/en/symptoms" class="btn btn--outline">&larr; All symptoms</a>
        <a href="/en/contact" class="btn btn--primary">Book an appointment</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>

<style>
  .hero-page { background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-navy) 0%, #1a3d6d 100%); padding: 6rem 0 4rem; color: var(--color-white); }
  .hero-page h1 { color: var(--color-white); font-size: 2.75rem; }
  .hero-sub { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.75); font-size: 1.15rem; margin-top: 1rem; }
  .detail-content { max-width: 800px; }
  .detail-icon { width: 80px; height: 80px; margin-bottom: 2rem; }
  .detail-content p { font-size: 1.05rem; line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; color: var(--color-gray); }
  .detail-cta { display: flex; gap: 1rem; margin-top: 3rem; flex-wrap: wrap; }
  @media (max-width: 768px) { .hero-page h1 { font-size: 2rem; } }
</style>
